NamespaceHandler
public class DellRoadStuffNamespaceHandler
extends NamespaceHandlerSupport

Spring NamespaceHandler for the dellroad-stuff XML namespace.

This adds support for the <dellroad-stuff:sql/> XML tag, which defines a SQLDatabaseAction bean, and the <dellroad-stuff:sql-update/> XML tag, which wraps the same thing in a SpringDelegatingSchemaUpdate bean.
